{"tid":1735224,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Poly手足只做3件事:棄裝、集糧、休息","createTime":"2019-11-18T13:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T15:58:08.000Z","uid":80972,"like":305,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"e9bc229406671f6b134916cbe07aef9fbaf2c056","tid":1735224,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"從來自首都係d狗最鐘意嘅把戲。我有個朋友幾年前俾人打，仲俾對面告返打人，落完口供d狗冇諗住查，反而叫你認罪，叫保釋你嘅親人勸你認罪。<span style=\"color: red;\">結果死唔認罪，最後因為證據不足所以告唔入。</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以大家千萬咪自守!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以必定要<span style=\"color: red;\">棄裝</span><br />\na) 留起室內唔好著 black block，要去手守先著<br />\nb) 收埋武器喺出入口，必要時先用，最好抹埋指紋<br />\n<br />\n一定要集糧<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">頂得幾耐得幾耐，</span>時間就係金錢，守得愈長，愈多時間救大家。時間愈長，社會嘅輿論會愈勁<br />\n<br />\n輸流休息<br />\n手足輪流把守同休息，唔好俾狗咁易入去。休息嘅時間<span style=\"color: red;\">互相鼓勵，有支持先有希望!</span><br />\n<br />\n最後糧盡水絕，就call白車，一齊入醫院，最少唔會俾人打48個鐘。<br />\n<br />\nPoly手足加油! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f35a03d0057e9f7aaa40f79d86609fbd1f5e4c","tid":1735224,"uid":80972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"Poly手足加油! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7aa4df230d81a43f8b37d000a9f970f1b33ed6c","tid":1735224,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c6f388f7a54cc860d2475d67808bc23b9ccf43e0","tid":1735224,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:37:54.000Z","msg":"Poly手足加油! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a5c30b7abf22b5f1637b4c01b2b76a2d13699f","tid":1735224,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:38:06.000Z"